text: Çaro () is a commune in the Pyrénées-Atlantiques department in south-western France. It is located in the former province of Lower Navarre. ==References== ==External links== * Quid entry Category:Communes of Pyrénées-Atlantiques Category:Lower Navarre Category:Pyrénées-Atlantiques communes articles needing translation from French Wikipedia
